{
  "stem": "23090.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was like the next day, because I don't-- I don't know how long these-- once you're in one of these boxcars, it's dark, and you're just in your own world.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you hear these-- these wheels on these tracks, da-da-da, da-da-da.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, that's all you hear, and you-- time doesn't mean anything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If you leave at night, you get there in the morning, maybe it's four hours later, or maybe it's a day later.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I tell you, I was not able to coordinate what was-- what time of day or night it was.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I would say it was either the next day or maybe several hours later.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so I got off the train, and we got into this camp called Kaufbeuren.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there, I met my next experience as to get beat up pretty good by a Kappo.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] He gave an order.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, you know, in a concentration camp, under-- under-- when they tell you to move, you better understand.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "If not, you're out of luck.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And this guy is screaming all kinds of things, and people are moving, and I'm standing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I don't know-- you know, I just didn't relate to what he was saying, and he just hit me with some kind of a rubber or something.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Of course, their favorite things were cow tails.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were burnt cow tails with knobs on them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So when you got whipped, it was like-- it was the-- the tail that was hardened with these-- with these knots on them, OK.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he hit me on my head, and I just completely got knocked out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I don't know when I-- I don't know when I came to, but when I came to, I was not the same.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
